New Simulations¶

  • Athena4.2 (not Athena++)
  • Uniform grid
  • Larger box
  • More realistic external gravity
  • Movie

Thermal feedback with star particles¶

  • Star partical creation conditions: (1) LP density threshold, (2) converging flow, (3) local potential minimum.
  • SN rate and FUV strength from population synthesis models assuming fully sample IMF (SLUG)
  • Clustered SNe + runaways
  • Use momentum feedback for Unresolved thermal SNe (in practice, most of them are resolved for 4pc resolution)

In [105]:
den={}
B={}
Bmag={}
den_part={}
Bmag_part={}
for l in ds.keys():
    den[l]=ds[l].read_all_data('density')
    B[l]=ds[l].read_all_data('magnetic_field')
    Bmag[l]=np.sqrt((B[l]**2).sum(axis=3))
    
    le=ds[l].domain['left_edge']
    re=ds[l].domain['right_edge']
    z=np.arange(le[2],re[2],ds[l].domain['dx'][2])
    zidx=np.where(np.abs(z)<=512)[0]
    den_part[l]=den[l][zidx[0]:zidx[-1],:,:]
    Bmag_part[l]=Bmag[l][zidx[0]:zidx[-1],:,:]
    print Bmag[l].shape,Bmag_part[l].shape

(1024, 256, 256) (256, 256, 256)
(512, 256, 256) (511, 256, 256)
In [82]:
def set_grid(fig):
    ImGrid = ImageGrid(fig, 111, nrows_ncols = (1, 2),
                           direction = "row",\
                           axes_pad = 0.1,\
                           label_mode = "L",\
                           share_all = True,\
                           cbar_location="right",\
                           cbar_mode="single",\
                           cbar_size="5%",\
                           cbar_pad="1%")
    return ImGrid

g=set_grid(fig)
for i,l in enumerate(keys):
    ax=g[i]
    le=ds[l].domain['left_edge']
    re=ds[l].domain['right_edge']
    u=unit[l]
    surf=(u['density']*u['length']).to('Msun/pc**2').value
    im=ax.imshow(den[l].sum(axis=0)*ds[l].domain['dx'][2]*surf,cmap=plt.cm.pink_r,
               extent=[le[0],re[0],le[1],re[1]],origin='lower',norm=LogNorm(vmin=1.,vmax=1.e2))
    if l is 'new':
        sp = pd.DataFrame(ds[l].read_starvtk())
        scatter_sp(sp,ax,axis=0,type='surf',runaway=False,kpc=False)
    ax.set_xlim(-512,512)
    ax.set_ylim(-512,512)

hv={}
hm={}
for l in ds.keys():
    u=unit[l]
    
    logd=np.log10(den_part[l].flatten())
    logb=np.log10(Bmag_part[l].flatten()*u['magnetic_field'].cgs.value*1.e6)
    hv[l]=np.histogram2d(logd,logb,bins=[200,100],range=[(-6,4),(-3,2)])
    hm[l]=np.histogram2d(logd,logb,bins=[200,100],
             weights=den_part[l].flatten(),range=[(-6,4),(-3,2)])

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
for i,l in enumerate(ds.keys()):
    ax=plt.subplot(2,1,i+1)
    h=hm[l]
    X, Y = np.meshgrid(h[1], h[2])
    im=ax.pcolormesh(X,Y,(h[0]/h[0].sum()).T,norm=LogNorm())
    im.set_clim(1.e-6,1.e-2)
    im.set_cmap(plt.cm.bone_r)
